dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: La Coruna, sheet 2. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 44.0000. South Decimal Degree 43.0000. East Decimal Degree -8.0000. West Decimal Degree -9.0000. Alternate title: La Coru~na, Spain: La Coru~na Province. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain, 1:50,000, Instituto Geografico, 1929-34; Spain, 1:100,000, Estado Mayor del Ejercito, sheet 7, 1917, and sheet 22, 1915; Spain 1:200,000, Cuartel General del Generalisismo, sheet 1, 1934 and sheet 11, 1935; Iberian Peninsula, 1:250,000, G.S.G.S., 1941; Spain and Portugal road map 1:400,000, AMS, third edition, sheet 41, 1942; Railways in Spain and Portugal 1:1,500,000, GSGS 1941, corrected from intelligence Reports, 1943-44; Partially revised from aerial photography, 1941, 1942 and 1943.".
